data.description: Lucrative Investment Property Opportunity in a prime location, South Fulton.  This property presents the perfect setting for a thriving rental venture once renovated, offering a combination of convenience and proximity to Hartsfield/Manard Jackson International Airport, shopping and more. This unique property features 2 levels.  The main level offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a 2 car garage. The basement is unfinished with entrance to a massive front and back yard a few sqft shy of 2 acres.  No HOA!  Don't miss out on this exceptional investment.! Whether you prefer to renovate the existing property or start from scratch, the choice is yours. This lot is Perfect for an investor or anyone looking for an amazing lot and or home with great bones to renovate with land. SOLD AS IS.
